#: C/index.page:90
msgid "To configure <app>MATE Terminal</app>, choose <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">Edit</gui><gui style=\"guimenuitem\">Current Profile</gui></guiseq>. To configure another profile that you set up choose <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">Edit</gui><gui style=\"guimenuitem\">Profiles</gui></guiseq>, select the profile you want to edit, then click <gui style=\"guibutton\">Edit</gui>."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າ <app>MATE Terminal</app>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">ແກ້ໄ"
"ຂ</gui><gui style=\"guimenuitem\">ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ປັດຈຸບັນ</gui></guiseq>. ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າໂປຣໄຟລ໌"
"ອື່ນທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຕັ້ງໄວ້ ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">ແກ້ໄຂ</gui><gui "
"style=\"guimenuitem\">ໂປຣໄຟລ໌</gui></guiseq>, ເລືອກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂ, ແລ້ວຄລິ"
"ກ <gui style=\"guibutton\">ແກ້ໄຂ</gui>."

